INSERT INTO `db_page` VALUES ('1', 'Company Profile', ';', '11', '&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.gokingcasting.com/uploadfile/2014/0529/20140529060213602.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;heightline24&quot; id=&quot;pagecontent&quot;&gt;      &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt; Wenzhou Goking Faucet Co. Ltd, established in 2005, is specializing in manufacturing and exporting various kinds of high-quality stainless steel bathroom sanitary ware and focusing on research and development of stainless steel faucets and showers production. Goking Faucet, located in Zhejiang, covers an area of 10,000 square meters production line with annual production capacity of more than 3,000 tons. As concerning about the health problem of drinking water, Goking Faucet has been striving for established a perfect production line and quality management system by its efforts. Meanwhile, the Company has always been constantly introducing advanced process technologies, professional technicians and equipment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;    The major products are stainless steel faucet including Kitchen Faucet, Basin Faucet, Shower Faucet, Bathtub Faucet, Drinking Faucet, Sink and Bathroom sanitary accessories, etc. The products are making of stainless steel as the mainly material, instead of traditional copper, iron and plastic faucet, which is provided with the superior performance on health, safety, durable, easy cleaning and maintenance and so on. Our products are exported to worldwide, such as U.S., Europe, Australia, and Asia, etc.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n    The guideline of the Company is: to create excellence in technology, quality and service. We keep improving product competitiveness and increasing customer satisfaction, to serve our customers with better quality and service. Goking Faucet sincerely welcomes customers from all over the world to visit and creates brilliant development of cooperation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;heightline24&quot;&gt; &lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '', '0');
